   "value": "Optional: verify projector properties\r\nFullSimplify[PiPlus . PiPlus == PiPlus]\r\nFullSimplify[PiMinus . PiMinus == PiMinus]\r\nFullSimplify[PiPlus . PiMinus == ConstantArray[0, {2, 2}]]\r\nFullSimplify[PiPlus + PiMinus == IdentityMatrix[2]]",
