   "kind": 2,
   "value": "Clear[k, p, n];\r\n\r\nexprPlus = n (-1/2 - Cos[k/2]/(2 Sqrt[2 - Sin[k/2]^2])) + p;\r\nexprMinus = n (-1/2 + Cos[k/2]/(2 Sqrt[2 - Sin[k/2]^2])) + p;\r\n\r\nsolPlus = FullSimplify[\r\n   Solve[exprPlus == 0, k],\r\n   Assumptions -> {n > 0, p ∈ Reals, n ∈ Reals}\r\n   ];\r\n\r\nsolMinus = FullSimplify[\r\n   Solve[exprMinus == 0, k],\r\n   Assumptions -> {n > 0, p ∈ Reals, n ∈ Reals}\r\n   ];\r\n\r\nsolPlus\r\nsolMinus\r\nTeXForm[solPlus]\r\nTeXForm[solMinus]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
