   "value": "Clear[x, p, n];\r\n\r\neq = (-1/2 - x/(2 Sqrt[1 + x^2])) + p/n == 0;\r\n\r\nxsol = FullSimplify[\r\n   Solve[eq, x],\r\n   Assumptions -> {n > 0, p ∈ Reals, n ∈ Reals}\r\n   ]\r\n\r\nksol = FullSimplify[\r\n   x /. xsol /. Rule -> (2 ArcCos[#2] &)\r\n]",
